title.narrative: NRM PASA – E3/FAB, E3/LU and E3/Water

description.narrative: (USAID Economic Growth, Education and Environment (E3)): This Participating Agency Service Agreement (PASA) will continue to provide services from the U.S. Department of Agriculture (USDA) which allows E3 offices to carry out key Agency functions and responsibilities. Under the PASA, USDA provides expertise to perform technical assistance, training, and information in the areas of forestry, biodiversity, land and resource management, rural-urban linkages, water, and coastal resources management.
